data.description: Contract Pending Contract pending - back up offers only. It's Autumn!  This townhouse is ready for you to enjoy hot apple cider or a pumpkin spice latte on the patio featured with this 3 bedroom 2 bath home!  Nestled on a corner lot in Springbrook, this home has an open concept floorplan - featuring a spacious living room with a fireplace for the cozy mornings and evenings.  Primary bedroom has 3/4 bathroom with a dual vanity and huge walk-in closet with ample storage.  Another bedroom with a full bath on the main level.  Finished basement ready for movie/game nights with a 3rd bedroom.  Roomy 2 car garage! AMA
